title: StubHub IPO Fizzles: Stock Closes Down 6.4% on First Day of Trading
summary: StubHub had a disappointing stock-market debut: The company, which operates the leading secondary-ticketing marketplace for live events, saw its shares close 6.4% below the IPO price Wednesday.
